      "processed_data_description": "The paper compiles literature Mott–Schottky-derived doping/trap densities, apparent flatband potentials, dark open-circuit potentials, and apparent device thicknesses into plotted datasets. These are processed/derived values extracted from published reports, not raw measurements. The authors also compute resolution-limit curves using analytical expressions and compare literature points against them.",
